nord stream , new gates for entry of russian gas to europe .
he is designed for supplies gas the equivalent of 30 million households .
more than 500 guests , including four heads of state and government participated in the last tuesday on the shores of the baltic sea , between orchestra and exquisite performance snacks , in the opening of the nord stream , new pipeline , which directly connects russia and germany under water .
on the new pipeline 27.5 million of additional cubic metres of gas will come every year in western europe for the first 1 224 km long pipeline connecting the leningrad region with earth mecklenburg - pomerania .
and the ability to build third pipeline at the same direction have already been discussed .
these two countries will lose part of its power : they will be harder to influence russia , threatening to shut down access to western european markets .
but the price of europe 's energy , because the project created a gap between eastern and western europe .
" this pipeline is part of cooperation with russia , this is a new artery that connects us organically , " said francois fillon , opening the gas pipeline , showing the extent to which large gas contracts are important and politically and economically .
" a hundred needed to remove or destroy as a precaution , " said jens mueller , a spokeswoman for the company 's north flow .
the pipeline is a long metal snake weighing , equal weight 242 эйфелевых towers , without breaks throughout its length , without вентилей and without service stations .
" in case of an accident we close the flow of gas less than a minute " , " said jens muller .
