сигароообразный apparatus is inside a 1 - meter diameter pipeline and presses forward flow of gas .
gas pipeline was designed to work for 50 years without any repairs .
these five companies created a joint venture , called the northern flow , which was commissioned to build and operate gas pipeline .
then gazprom gave the company leases the twenty years with the possibility of extension of the entire gas transportation .
gas pipeline construction financing was provided by 30 % shareholders and 70 % bank credits .
pipeline out of the baltic sea in lubmin on a sandy beach , засаженный coniferous trees .
